product_name: Outside Inside Cabin Ornament Set - Set of 4 - 2012/2013 Closeout
long_description: Incredible detail gives the 4 ornaments of the Outside Inside Cabin Ornament Set a rustic, realistic appearance that will look great on your Christmas tree for years to come. Set of 4 ornaments includes an old-school outhouse, vintage canoe, Adirondack chair and a loon. Made of polystone resin with a braided cord for hanging from the tree. Closeout.
